title: Coconut and walnut oat biscuits
ingredients: ['250g plain flour, sifted', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', 'Pinch of salt', '225g butter, softened', '225g brown sugar', '200g sugar', '2 eggs, beaten', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '135g (1 1/2 cups) porridge oats', '110g walnuts, chopped', '75g desiccated coconut']
